    Raw -->|"Read latest response"| Transform
    Transform -->|"Write structured rows"| Normalized

    Normalized -->|"Look up upcoming game IDs"| PlayerProps
    OddsAPI -->|"Fetch player props per game"| PlayerProps
    PlayerProps -->|"Store raw + normalized props"| DB

    Ingest -->|"Success / failure alert"| Slack
    PlayerProps -->|"Success / failure alert"| Slack
